rows.label: tlk70000016_05_msg0001
rows.name:
I heard you guys helped
Freja get better!

rows.label: tlk70000016_05_msg0002
rows.name:
It was really making her mum sad,
having her sick all the time. And
she's gloomy enough, to be honest...

rows.label: tlk70000016_05_msg0003
rows.name:
But now she's always smiling! I
think she's even happier than
she was before Freja got sick.

rows.label: tlk70000016_05_msg0004
rows.name:
Freja still says the bugs I
catch are gross, though... I
guess some things never change.

rows.label: tlk70000016_05_msg0005
rows.name:
Thanks for helping Freja, and for
helping me, and well, all of us
really! You guys are the best.
